OL,3,CEx-Scotland rugby captain Stuart Hogg
OL,4,Chanded second community order
OL,6,FFormer Scotland rugby union captain
OL,7,FStuart Hogg has been handed a
OL,8,Fcommunity payback order after he
OL,9,Fadmitted abusing his estranged wife
OL,10,Fover the course of five years.
OL,12,FHe pleaded guilty to a single charge
OL,13,Fof domestic abuse of his ex-partner,
OL,14,FGillian Hogg, when he appeared at
OL,15,FSelkirk Sheriff Court in November last
OL,16,Fyear.
