OL,3,CEx-Scotland rugby captain Stuart Hogg
OL,4,Chanded second community order
OL,6,FHe's now been ordered to community
OL,7,Fpayback with one year of supervision
OL,8,Falong with a second five-year non-
OL,9,Fharassment order when he appeared at
OL,10,FSelkirk Sheriff Court for sentencing
OL,11,Fon 9 January 2025.
OL,13,FHogg admitted to tracking her
OL,14,Fmovements, shouting and swearing, and
OL,15,Fsending her messages which were
OL,16,Fdistressing in nature.
