OL,3,CEx-Scotland rugby captain Stuart Hogg
OL,4,Chanded second community order
OL,6,FThe 32-year-old, from Hawick, has
OL,7,Falready been banned from approaching
OL,8,For contacting Mrs Hogg for five years
OL,9,Fafter admitting to breach of his bail
OL,10,Fconditions after repeatedly contacting
OL,11,Fher in June 2024 - one night he sent
OL,12,Fher 28 messages.
OL,14,FSheriff Peter Paterson also fined him
OL,15,F#600 with an additional #40 victim
OL,16,Fsurcharge at Jedburgh Sheriff Court on
OL,17,F5 December 2024.
