OL,3,CEx-Scotland rugby captain Stuart Hogg
OL,4,Chanded second community order
OL,6,FHogg was due to be sentenced in
OL,7,FDecember 2024 but it was deferred to
OL,8,Fclarify whether a community order with
OL,9,Fremotely monitored supervision could
OL,10,Fbe imposed, as Hogg now lives abroad.
OL,12,FHogg now plays professional rugby for
OL,13,FMontpellier on a two-year contract. He
OL,14,Fmoved to France after announcing his
OL,15,Freturn from retirement last summer.
