OL,3,CEx-Scotland rugby captain Stuart Hogg
OL,4,Chanded second community order
OL,6,FIn relation to the domestic abuse
OL,7,Fcharge, the court previously heard the
OL,8,F32-year-old berated Mrs Hogg for "not
OL,9,Fbeing fun" after going on drinking
OL,10,Fbinges with his colleagues, and once
OL,11,Fsent more than 200 text messages to
OL,12,Fher in the space of a few hours.
OL,14,FHe had been due to stand trial at the
OL,15,Fsame court in November 2024 but
OL,16,Fpleaded guilty that day to a charge of
OL,17,Fdomestic abuse between 2019 and 2024
OL,18,Fat locations including Hawick,
OL,19,FScottish Borders. The court heard that
OL,20,Fday he is in the process of a divorce.
