OL,3,CEx-Scotland rugby captain Stuart Hogg
OL,4,Chanded second community order
OL,6,FIn 2022, Mrs Hogg went on a night out
OL,7,Fand was bombarded with text messages
OL,8,Ffrom her husband which "caught the
OL,9,Fattention of the people she was with",
OL,10,Fthe court heard.
OL,12,FHogg used an app to track his wife
OL,13,Fafter their move to Hawick in 2023. He
OL,14,Fwould 'question her whereabouts' while
OL,15,Fshe dropped the children off, Mr Long
OL,16,Ftold the court.
OL,18,FIn that year Mrs Hogg decided to leave
OL,19,Fthe rugby player and sought advice
OL,20,Ffrom a domestic abuse service.
