OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F358A1736864720
OL,3,CEx-Scotland rugby captain Stuart Hogg
OL,4,Chanded second community order
OL,6,FThe court heard that in September
OL,7,F2023, Hogg sent so many messages it
OL,8,Fled Mrs Hogg to have a panic attack,
OL,9,Fand Hogg "sent in excess of 200 texts
OL,10,Fin a few hours despite being asked to
OL,11,Fleave her alone".
OL,13,FOn February 21 last year, police were
OL,14,Fcalled due to Hogg "shouting and
OL,15,Fswearing" and he was taken into
OL,16,Fcustody and then placed on a bail
OL,17,Forder stipulating not to contact Mrs
OL,18,FHogg, or to enter the family home.
