OL,6,FShe said: "The Crown Office and
OL,7,FProcurator Fiscal Service recognises
OL,8,Fthe devastating impact of domestic
OL,9,Fabuse and is committed to the robust
OL,10,Fprosecution of offences, regardless of
OL,11,Fwho the offender is.
OL,13,F"No-one should have to live in fear of
OL,14,Fa partner or former partner. The
OL,15,Ftrauma suffered by victims ` and
OL,16,Fchildren who witness these crimes ` is
OL,17,Fsignificant.
OL,19,F"I would urge anyone affected by
OL,20,Fsimilar offending to come forward and
OL,21,Freport it.
